column10: Do you know how ranking algorithms work in general?
column12: Q1. Clarity of Ranking Mechanism: Tripadvisor's documentation clearly and sufficiently explains the mechanics and main parameters of the ranking system.
column13: Q2. Rationale for Ranking Parameters: Tripadvisor's documentation satisfactorily clarifies why certain parameters are critical in determining ranking instead of others.
column14: Q3. Improving Ranking: Tripadvisor's documentation adequately instructs users on how to improve the ranking of their goods or services.
column15: Q4. Altering Ranking Through Payments: Tripadvisor's documentation transparently discloses the paid options to improve ranking, and the effects thereof.
